text: The Oceanids are the daughters of the Titans Oceanus and Tethys in Greek mythology. They are water and ocean nymphs. Also Oceanids can mean all the children of Oceanus and Tethys, which includes the other water and river gods. Among them are: *Klymene *Metis *Pleione *Styx Category:Nymphs de:Okeanide en:Oceanid
title: Oceanid
